Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:33.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,One hundred ten years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.23,0:01:35.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the Thirteen Court Guard Squads\Nof that day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.36,0:01:36.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,were different from the present,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.87,0:01:39.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but there were some\Nvery familiar faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.86,0:01:43.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The captain of Squad 5 was\NShinji Hirako, who currently
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.70,0:01:46.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,resides in the World of the Living\Nas a Visored.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.20,0:01:50.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Other members of the Visored\Nalso held positions
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.26,0:01:53.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,as captains and lieutenants\Nin the Thirteen Court Guard Squads.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:56.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,At the time,\NKisuke Urahara became
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.94,0:02:00.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the captain of Squad 12\Nupon the recommendation of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.84,0:02:03.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Squad 2 captain,\NYoruichi Shihoin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.80,0:02:06.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am considering creating\Nan organization
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.30,0:02:08.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,under the control of\NSquad 12
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.84,0:02:10.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,unlike anything ever seen\Nin the Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.79,0:02:13.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm calling it the "Department of\NResearch and Development."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.95,0:02:18.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to assume the seat\Nof deputy department head.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.79,0:02:23.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurotsuchi Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:26.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,At about the same time\Nat the Kuchiki Clan residence,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:29.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,a young Byakuya practiced\Nhis swordsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:31.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,At Squad 13's barracks,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:34.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaien Shiba was being persuaded\Nby Jushiro Ukitake
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:37.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to be promoted to lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.53,0:02:43.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Each, with their own motives,\Nspent their days thinking of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.11,0:02:46.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the future of the Soul Society and\Nthe Thirteen Court Guard Squads.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:51.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But glimpses of the start of\Na nightmare were already showing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:54.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:56.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your skill is even better\Nthan I had heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.76,0:03:00.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How was our Third Seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.34,0:03:03.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Awful. No competition at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:05.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.23,0:03:08.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.53,0:03:13.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,After swinging\Nback to the past and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.91,0:03:16.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,giving a glimpse of\Na moment in time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:19.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the pendulum swings\Nseveral years forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:23.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The incident occurred\Nnine years
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:26.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,after Kisuke Urahara\Nbecame captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.63,0:04:33.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:34.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:36.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,'Morning, Hirako.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:39.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I said you can call me Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:41.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.56,0:04:45.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,'Morning, Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:51.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to be less casual\Nand call me Kurotsuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:53.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You are an irritating fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:04:57.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:05:01.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way,\Nhave you heard about that story?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:03.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:06.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:10.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What was that for, Hiyori?!\NAll of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:12.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't greeted me yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:16.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with greeting the other two\Nand leaving me out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:19.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to greet you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:26.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This mouth! This damn mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:32.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes, Captain Urahara,\Nhave you already heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.30,0:05:34.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Heard about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:38.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,About the violent deaths\Nin the Rukon district.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:38.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:40.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I was talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:42.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Good follow up, Sosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.12,0:05:44.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Violent deaths?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:45.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.13,0:05:49.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In the past month or so, there have\Nbeen a series of incidents where
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.04,0:05:51.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,residents of the Rukon district\Nhave been disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:53.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason is unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:54.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.86,0:05:57.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, they went somewhere\Nand never came back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:06:01.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?\NYou call that running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.06,0:06:05.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If they ran away, who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:06.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They can do whatever they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:10.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is different.\NThey literally "disappear."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:13.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Gone, without a trace,\Nleaving only their clothes behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.01,0:06:17.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If they died and became spirits,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:18.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the clothes they were wearing\Nwould disappear as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:20.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:25.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They vanished alive,\Nunable to retain human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:28.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only explanation\NI can think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:32.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Alive, but unable to retain\Nhuman form?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:37.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'm just telling you exactly\Nwhat I heard from Captain Unohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:39.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.03,0:06:46.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, Squad 9 is\Nalready there to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:58.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:07:00.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening to me, Kensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:05.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "unknown"?\NTell me, Kensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:09.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet! Unknown means unknown!\NQuit babbling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:11.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:13.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for\Na captain to go
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:15.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,just to investigate\Nsomething unknown!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:18.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unknown, that's why\Nwe're going to check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:22.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,An advance party went out!\NTen people!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.09,0:07:24.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You could've just waited\Nfor them to report,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.49,0:07:26.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but you're so impatient, Kensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:27.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You show off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:29.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Lieutenant, please, you're doing it again.\N– I'm sick of this…sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:32.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Captain! Please calm down, Captain!\N– Stupid Kensei, you show off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:34.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– You know she's always like that!\N– Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:35.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:37.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,when did I ever tell you\Nto come along?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:41.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to come along!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:43.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home, take a crap,\Nand go to sleep, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:49.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your lieutenant, so I always\Nhave to be with my captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:52.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the stupid one for\Nnot knowing that, Kensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:54.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:55.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Captain!\N– Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:07:58.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.09,0:07:59.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.34,0:08:00.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to eat ohagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:02.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The kind with kinako\Non the outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:05.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– What should we do, Captain?\N– Nothing but kinako ohagi will do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.30,0:08:07.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Ignore her!\N– I want the big kinako ohagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:28.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't get away,{\i0}\NI'll end up like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.83,0:08:31.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to get away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.69,0:08:36.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I can't yell.{\i0}\NMy legs won't move.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.27,0:08:38.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:47.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:48.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:49.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:51.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:09:00.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Faster! Run faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:11.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:13.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to get away right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:26.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:28.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's enormous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:32.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:33.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:35.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:50.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:52.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot… It won't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:53.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.30,0:10:30.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hurry and get away!\NYou don't want to die, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:37.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Back off, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:38.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Yes, sir!\N– Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:52.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:10:59.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachikaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:42.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everybody all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.39,0:11:43.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Yes, sir!\N– Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:57.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What're you crying for, kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:12:00.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're alive.\NYou should be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:04.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:07.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's asking too much, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:08.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:11.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, stand up, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:18.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:23.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu…Shuhei…Hisagi…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.83,0:12:25.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuhei, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:28.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a strong-sounding name.\NStop crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:34.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you crying again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.66,0:12:36.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I said stop crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:38.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:42.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.73,0:12:44.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:46.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell did you go\Nduring the battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:50.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In those bushes!\NI found this on the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:52.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,See? A shihakusho!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.62,0:13:03.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There were a whole bunch\Nof these here! Ten of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.48,0:13:07.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten…shihakusho?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.86,0:13:11.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, they must be…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:16.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What, what?\NAre ten sets important? Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:18.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.81,0:13:23.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It matches the number\Nin the advance party!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:27.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! But these were\Ntaken off over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:31.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How could they have been taken off\Nwith the sash still tied?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:34.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How could they have\Ntaken off their tabi socks
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.26,0:13:35.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,with their sandals still on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:40.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Eishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:40.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:42.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Contact Central 46!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:44.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Souls have vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:46.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We have our first\NSoul Reaper casualties!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:47.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:48.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Todo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:48.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:51.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a possibility of\Nan unknown pathogen
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:52.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that disintegrates souls!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:56.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Request that Squad 12\Nsend lab personnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:56.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:58.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kasaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:13:58.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:01.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Have the main squad\Nstanding by and send tents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:04.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll set up camp here tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.35,0:14:05.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:09.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is the work of an enemy\Ntargeting Soul Reapers,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.00,0:14:11.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,they will eventually\Ntarget the Seireitei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:16.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll crush them here before\Nthey get near the Seireitei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:17.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Yes, sir!\N– Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:18.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:22.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:25.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We're checking the area.\NCome with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:29.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid! You go on home!\NBefore it gets dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:33.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:48.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you serious\Nabout camping out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:51.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Will there be ohagi\Nfor dessert?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:53.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No. If you want some,\Nget it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.46,0:14:55.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kensei, you're a butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.28,0:15:19.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice. Very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.37,0:15:24.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I'm still waiting for\Ncontainer number 22!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:30.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still over there?!\NHurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:33.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,For goodness sake,\Nat this rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:34.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be dark before\Nyou bring it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.71,0:15:38.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:40.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was being nice\Nand helping you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:42.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so that's no way to talk to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:45.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, you worm!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:48.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you so angry\Nabout all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:52.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That side of you,\Nquite honestly, is a turn off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:54.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I said shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:58.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to assist you\Nin the first place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:00.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:03.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your rank? Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:05.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:08.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no need for\Nsuch a thing as rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:10.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.14,0:16:11.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're third! Third!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:13.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.23,0:16:16.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the lieutenant!\NYou're third!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:19.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't order me around!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:21.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:24.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Here at the Department of Research\Nand Development,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.73,0:16:28.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the deputy department head,\Nand you are the laboratory chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:30.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I outrank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.53,0:16:32.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist on\Nfollowing squad rules,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:36.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,then as long as you're here,\Nyou must obey me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:38.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.48,0:16:40.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.05,0:16:44.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it now?\NPlease try to be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:47.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had much sleep, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:49.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something about this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:51.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't taught him well!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:52.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:55.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.92,0:16:57.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.89,0:17:00.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a prototype of a new gigai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:03.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You remember what\NHirako said this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:06.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,About the incidents\Nin the Rukon district
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.16,0:17:08.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,where he believes people\Nwere unable to retain human form,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:10.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and their souls would vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:13.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Supposing that what\Nhe says is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:15.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that if we were to\Nplace a soul
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:18.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that was on the verge of\Ndisintegration into a human mold,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.96,0:17:20.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the soul would not vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:23.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to see if I could apply\Ngigai technology
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:25.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,into making that mold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:27.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:31.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:34.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Izaemon Todo,\NSixth Seat of Squad 9!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:38.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kisuke Urahara,\Ncaptain of Squad 12 here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:42.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have come to convey a request\Nfrom Kensei Muguruma,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.76,0:17:44.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,captain of Squad 9!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:53.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:54.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:57.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will select personnel immediately\Nand send them on their way tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.10,0:17:58.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:01.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,please go back and\Nhelp Muguruma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:04.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!\NThank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:07.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.37,0:18:10.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard him, so…\NHiyori, please go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.83,0:18:12.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:15.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not send someone\Nlower in rank?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.81,0:18:17.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All you do is complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.42,0:18:20.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If everything is\Ndisagreeable to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.90,0:18:22.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,why not quit being a lieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:25.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so disrespectful,\NAkon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:26.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're asking for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:29.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ready, deputy department head.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:30.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.81,0:18:32.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This really pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:34.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:36.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiyori, you're the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:39.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can confidently entrust\Na task like this to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.21,0:18:44.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's anything\Nyou think you'll need,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:47.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,you can take it,\Neven from the captain's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:52.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A sample from the site of\Nthe vanishing souls
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:54.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,will be very valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.83,0:18:57.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Hiyori.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:01.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:08.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna demand more\Nfor expenses later!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:09.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.86,0:19:14.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let anyone know\Nabout that, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:30.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What took you so long, Todo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:31.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.59,0:19:33.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the only one who\Nwent directly to the barracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:35.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.31,0:19:39.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll relieve you.\NGo inside and rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:41.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so lax?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:44.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you're back,\Nthe three of us will keep watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:46.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take turns,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:48.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,one man at a time,\Nevery two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:51.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, Kasaki is resting inside\Nwith the captain and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:53.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You take watch over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:55.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:15.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How could she fall asleep\Nso nonchalantly
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.45,0:20:18.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,under conditions like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:20.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, your collar's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:25.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kensei, you pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're annoying even in your sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.46,0:20:28.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to whack you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.05,0:20:32.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:47.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Todo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:49.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:57.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Todo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:20:58.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.31,0:21:00.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your guard up, Kasaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.16,0:21:02.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is still nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:05.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro! Wake up, Mashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.72,0:21:11.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kasaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:29.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:42.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.30,0:23:23.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hirako, why was\NSquad 9 sent to investigate?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.90,0:23:26.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kensei and Mashiro are\Nconstantly fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:27.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so noisy,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.24,0:23:29.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the Head Captain hasn't been\Ngetting much sleep lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.18,0:23:30.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's part of his solution\Nto the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.60,0:23:34.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really? Look who's talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.13,0:23:37.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Substitute Soul Reaper\NWork Journal!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.08,0:23:43.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Found her?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.91,0:23:44.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.74,0:23:48.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! How far did she go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.68,0:23:51.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll search over there next!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.04,0:23:52.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.63,0:23:55.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Searching for Soul Reapers
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.78,0:23:58.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,who forgot their Soul Phone\Nand came to the World of the Living
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.47,0:24:02.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,is an important job of\NSubstitute Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.62,0:24:05.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsumoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.02,0:24:07.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,